dc_creator_sm: Yolo County, Public Works Division, Planning Services
dc_description_s: These boundaries were derived from "heads-up" digitizing based on the Census Boundaries. The best attempt was made to translate the boundary lines to the base map boundary lines of Yolo County. Interpretation was necessary in many places where Census boundary lines did not match and "real world" lines. For a copy of the Official GIS layer of these boundaries, please contact the Yolo Coynty Elections Department (530) 666-8133
dc_title_s: Board of Supervisor Districts, Yolo County, California, 2011
